freetext.HEALTHCARE_VISITS_OTHER: I shared the tremor videos w a clinician, was told to monitor it and hope it disappears.
freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Dizzy at standing multiple times a day; hand/finger tremors (recorded these) off and on all day; and a good part of yesterday evening I felt shaky all over, like albuterol side effect? Only I hadnt used it.
Abdominal rash last night at 10p (benedryl resolved it), burning skin feeling all day today, dizzy and faint feeling when standing
Dizzy feeling when I stand up, lost ability to taste sour things - like bold salt and vinegar almonds are my fave and they didnt really have a flavor at all except sugary almonds.
Dizzy when I stand; drinking 16oz of water every hour most hours Im awake.
Shaking again, all day 7a-2p; skin burning feeling, headache, dizzy and faint when standing and walking (no matter how much I hydrate)
